(In reply to Cy Schubert from comment #18)
Also need:
1) savestate/restore without manual rebuild the world;
2) GUI (Qt);
3) WebGUI like phpvirtualbox;
4) support run with different disk formats like VDI, VMDK and etc without converting;
5) support work on CPU with VT-x without UG (Unrestricted Guest) - Nehalems, Penryns, Conroes, some lowend mobile/atom based;
6) support boot in BIOS mode without UEFI;
7) support hotswap passthrough of single USB device;
. . .
